metadata.name: Oversharing
metadata.description:
There's a fine line between oversharing and being authentic. However, when it comes to explosions of ideas, inspiration and colors it should be let out into the world. This is the first artwork of the Extrusions collection by the Danish visual artist and architect Anne Gade. The artwork was created using digital drawing tools to 'paint' abstract color compositions. Then it was digitally processed through several applications.  

Size: 2048 x 2048 px
